          "tables": []
        },
        "Subsequent_symptoms": {
          "text": "Chills (rarely rigors)\nCough\nAbdominal distension\nConstipation (more common than diarrhea)\n“Rose spots” – truncal light red macular rash (in the 2nd wk)\nHepatosplenomegaly\nGI bleeding\nTransaminitis\nLeukopenia with left shift (adults)\nLeukocytosis (children)",
